| Dahl, O.M.; Wolthusen, S.D.                                                                                                     | Modeling and Execution of Complex Attack Scenarios using Interval Timed Colored Petri Nets                                           | This paper described a mechanism for the modeling, partial analysis, and automatic execution of multi-agent, multi-stage attacks based on interval timed colored Petri nets. It suggests a possible research direction to address concurrent attack paths and attack agents.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  |
